{
  "title": "Lightly Indulgent Chinese Asparagus Stir Fry",
  "description": "A yeasty and springy Chinese dish featuring white asparagus, this stir fry is a delicious and indulgent treat. It is a jain friendly dish that is perfect for a weeknight dinner.",
  "cuisine": "Chinese",
  "diet": [
